g"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "108 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/435920418"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9snwlZy586xfEAMaCDU5MTUwMzQ1IPm+g/8FMAA4ZEAFcgk0MzU5MjA0MTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1730985965.340636", "card_id": "Q_3332001682", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 519}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日媒预测日本今年新生儿跌破 70 万，越来越多日本人选择不婚或晚婚，反映了什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "日本政府 5 日发布今年上半年新生儿人口数据，较去年同期减少大约 6%，继续呈下降趋势。媒体推断，日本今年新生儿人数将首次跌破 70 万人。 厚生劳动省发布的人口动态统计显示，日本今年 1 至 6 月新生儿为 329998 人，比去年同期减少 6.3%。这一数据不包括在日外国人。基于这一趋势，日本媒体普遍预期，今年全年新生儿人口将首次少于 70 万。去年日本新生儿大约为 72.7 万，连续八年创新低。 厚生劳动省人口动态数据还显示，日本今年上半年死亡人数比去年同期增加 1.8%，为 800274 人，从而人口自然减少逾 47 万人。日本媒体报道，出生率持续下降，反映出越来越多日本人选择不婚或晚婚，以及晚育的趋势。（新华社）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-588ed8975cd2debd53585a331ccebaf8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "106 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3332001682"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI9snwlZy586xfEAMaCTExMTY0Mjk4MCD9y6y5BjAAOKIIQAZyCjMzMzIwMDE2ODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1730985965.341436", "card_id": "Q_3429814164", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《再见爱人》第四季第四期？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本期的夫妻画像环节让三对嘉宾们彼此「看见」了吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec6c0f421748f6c2882fe1674961e3c9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "bac